{"tid":1319437,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港係咪已經出現咗恐怖組織","createTime":"2019-07-15T07:08:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T07:17:21.000Z","uid":34136,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"acc0fda7cd66fc1fb6b523fa12ceaaa5d6340bb3","tid":1319437,"uid":34136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T07:08:09.000Z","msg":"呢個激進組織使用大量暴力，企圖以恐怖手法推翻香港嘅核心價值。<br />\n<br />\n該組織勢力龐大，絕對不可輕視。其牽涉案件包括長洲警署殺警案、利希慎槍殺案、雙十暴動、 三狼案翻案、1966年九龍騷動、 錦田殺警案、 血洗水警輪案、蘇屋邨山坡姦殺案、尖沙咀警員被槍殺案、 警員鄭東昇案、半山卑利士路殺警案、葵涌警察宿舍B座510室四屍滅門命案、 葵涌警署大樓開槍案、王德輝綁架案、入境事務大樓縱火案，等等嘅香港大小案件均有該組織嘅身影。<br />\n<br />\n其涉獵範圍曾經或現在包括謀殺、施放毒氣、酷刑、間諜、收藏軍火、嫖妓、貪污、暴動、打鬥、恐嚇、索取金錢（俗稱差餉）、地下賭博等，令人髮指的罪行。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n懷疑爲該組織的恐怖份子蒙面現身街頭，未知是否打算持槍掃射 （圖片來源：蘋果日報）<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20080208/large/08la5p11n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20080208%2Flarge%2F08la5p11n.jpg&h=d92df360&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據說該組織成員多爲未受教育人士，受外國激進勢力煽動不滿而破壞社會安寧。<br />\n<br />\n擔任指揮官的外國勢力（圖片來源：蘋果日報）<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/pBamzSk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FpBamzSk.png&h=dfa65f64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據說組織的總司令亦曾被指擁有英國護照（圖片來源：BBC）<img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/16A1B/production/_107799629_hi055183171.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F624%2Fcpsprodpb%2F16A1B%2Fproduction%2F_107799629_hi055183171.jpg&h=2302b634&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n疑爲外國成員<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.vjmedia.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/04/163503/19702377_1555165131222671_1424124733224477276_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vjmedia.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2F04%2F163503%2F19702377_1555165131222671_1424124733224477276_n.jpg&h=70ebae4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其歷史上多次意圖以暴力攻擊政府部門，意圖破壞香港繁榮穩定。<br />\n<br />\n攻擊廉署總部<br />\n<img src=\"http://ubeat.com.cuhk.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/111ICAC5-300x207.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fubeat.com.cuhk.edu.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F111ICAC5-300x207.jpg&h=0a80ef27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在內應協助下持槍進入立法會<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpO6L8m5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpO6L8m5.jpg&h=dfa07876&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除武裝襲擊外，該組織成員亦經常進行示威，並有大量隱形成員現身支持。<br />\n<br />\n一次集會，該組織成員宣稱逾38,000名成員參加，現場所見，該組織必定已經發明出隱形戰鬥服。<br />\n<img src=\"http://himg2.huanqiu.com/attachment2010/2017/0223/20170223012707685.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhimg2.huanqiu.com%2Fattachment2010%2F2017%2F0223%2F20170223012707685.jpg&h=48b6d0d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n於彌敦道上遊行導致80歲孕婦未能及時送往律敦治產房（圖片來源：立場新聞）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/66162451_9A6wm_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F66162451_9A6wm_1200x0.jpg&h=dda037dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根據1925年國際社會簽署的日內瓦議定書，各締約國同意在戰爭中不使用窒息性、毒性或其他氣體，以及使用一切類似的液體、物體或器件，即化學武器與生物武器。締約國於1925年6月17日在瑞士日內瓦簽署了該協議，於1928年2月8日開始生效。唯該組織多次大量使用不得於戰爭中使用的武器。<br />\n<br />\n該組織多次針對平民使用化學武器，有記錄的襲擊包括1967年、1984年、1989年、2005年、2014年、2019年，並據稱有計劃地多次針對香港的越南裔人士發動襲擊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1462411_1_L_20190612190933.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1462411_1_L_20190612190933.jpg&h=86f649e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖片來源：香港電台）<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1462361_1_L_20190612162447.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1462361_1_L_20190612162447.jpg&h=4fb47d3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n恐怖組織組織嚴密，行事極爲兇狠，包括於空中爆破毒氣彈<br />\n<img src=\"http://faith100.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Umbrella-revolution.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffaith100.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2FUmbrella-revolution.jpg&h=921b43d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n於密集人羣中突然施放（圖片來源：AM730）<br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2017/2/1488278027_Og-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2017%2F2%2F1488278027_Og-1280w.jpg&h=4c27c3db&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n使用生物武器（圖片來源：蘋果日報）<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20120803/large/03la6p05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20120803%2Flarge%2F03la6p05.jpg&h=aff7eff4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不斷對平民使用生物武器，行徑恐怖<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.chinapress.com.my/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/HONG_KONG-CHINA-POLITICS-CRIME-588874.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinapress.com.my%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F06%2FHONG_KONG-CHINA-POLITICS-CRIME-588874.jpg&h=45d25bf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港多宗爆炸案均有恐怖組織成員的身影出現於現場。<br />\n<br />\n組織炸彈專家處理炸彈，並公然於社交媒體上展示<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/5b4N5Fsl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F5b4N5Fsl.jpg&h=d8d85590&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n成員於爆炸後離開現場 （圖片來源：蘋果日報）<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/files/imagecache/w456/column_images/905994_10153762806527506_1457540080356775149_o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Ffiles%2Fimagecache%2Fw456%2Fcolumn_images%2F905994_10153762806527506_1457540080356775149_o.jpg&h=1c7964c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n薯仔堆內藏手榴彈<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20190203/s00007/da35ddd4cc4a514e9e848c0a3744902b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20190203%2Fs00007%2Fda35ddd4cc4a514e9e848c0a3744902b.jpg&h=d17f8ad1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成員於網上步操宣示力量<br />\n<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2019/01/14/0/048d36ccf4ca7b4ca2bcb8dc176de982.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2019%2F01%2F14%2F0%2F048d36ccf4ca7b4ca2bcb8dc176de982.jpg&h=9c9d9f06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n成員意圖帶平民女性回組織基地成交，更警告受害人不可嗌出聲<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D_GDlppU4AAPVCq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FD_GDlppU4AAPVCq.jpg&h=1a317a07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n成員裝成警察，被聰明的香港人智破<br />\n[img]<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/yHBHAUZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FyHBHAUZ.png&h=79a5bf39&s={SIZE}\" />[/img]<br />\n<br />\n公然網上展示非法武器<br />\n<img src=\"http://image.wenweipo.com/2018/07/08/a09a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.wenweipo.com%2F2018%2F07%2F08%2Fa09a.jpg&h=1387c213&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n面目猙獰<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/929575/org/82ba48920b867953252522d2689160e3.jpg/EvsCT_Fcm1AfnqWDvzqQPuvrY8wAgaP-dEAIV3RACFc?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F929575%2Forg%2F82ba48920b867953252522d2689160e3.jpg%2FEvsCT_Fcm1AfnqWDvzqQPuvrY8wAgaP-dEAIV3RACFc%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=84640882&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鬼鬼鼠鼠偷番薯（圖片來源：Facebook 九十後社會紀實）<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Po07cIu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FPo07cIu.png&h=503bde20&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/wUdiVYb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FwUdiVYb.png&h=8465235f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">If You See Something, Say Something&reg;</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">謹此聲明：香港市民譴責恐怖組織嘅一切暴力同恐怖行爲，恥與爲伍</span></span>"},{"pid":"344cb00ed15568224cddc3ec79fbf4e46c3157af","tid":1319437,"uid":26045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T07:12:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n屌你句caption<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成員於爆炸後離開現場 （圖片來源：蘋果日報）<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/files/imagecache/w456/column_images/905994_10153762806527506_1457540080356775149_o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Ffiles%2Fimagecache%2Fw456%2Fcolumn_images%2F905994_10153762806527506_1457540080356775149_o.jpg&h=1c7964c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</blockquote>"},{"pid":"d8f04a4b129088d38d32e9e22b7a36a0d51c7030","tid":1319437,"uid":122134,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T07:17:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://puui.qpic.cn/qqvideo_ori/0/a0558u26fpi_496_280/0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpuui.qpic.cn%2Fqqvideo_ori%2F0%2Fa0558u26fpi_496_280%2F0&h=38726df2&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}